name: Marcus Kingley
profile_summary: The user is a 31-year-old white caucasian man, 6'0" in height, located in Los Angeles for dating but originally from New York. His key values are authenticity, ambition, and mindfulness and his interests include hiking, traveling, reading classic literature, basketball, and dining. Currently, he subscribes to agnostic religious beliefs and liberal political views. His option for sexual orientation is straight, prefers monogamy, and is seeking a life partner. He doesn't have kids but wants them someday. User identifies with he/him/his pronouns, doesn't own any pets, and his zodiac sign is Taurus. With no smoking, no marijuana and no drug habits, he takes drinks sometimes and maintains an active exercise regime. As per MBTI, his personality type is ENTJ.
